title: Phantom Planet - Raise the Dead (2008)
description:
Raise the Dead is the 4th studio album from Phantom Planet, an alternative rock band best known by their song "California" which was the theme song for the TV show "The OC". The CD was officially released on April 15, 2008 through the upcoming record label Fueled By Ramen. The CD includes a reworked version of Leader, which appeared on the Limited Edition Tour EP. The first single from the CD is "Do the Panic". Enjoy and please seed!
